Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 09:11:24 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Add structured career data layer (phase 2)

- Add /data JSON files for projects, certifications, experience, education, awards
- Add lib/types.ts with shared TypeScript interfaces
